<topic id="properties-view">
  <title>Properties View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>SVN Client<indexterm>Views<indexterm>Properties view</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The properties view presents <ph keyref="apacheSubversion"/> properties for the currently
      selected resource from either the <uicontrol>Working Copy</uicontrol> view or the
        <uicontrol>Repositories</uicontrol> view. <ph conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/reopen-view"
      /></p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <title>Properties View</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_svn_properties_view.png" placement="inline"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>The table includes four columns:<ul>
        <li>
          <p><uicontrol>State</uicontrol> - Can be one of the following:<ul>
              <li>
                <p><i>(empty)</i> - Normal unmodified property (same current and base values)</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><i>* (asterisk)</i> - Modified property (current and base values are
                  different)</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><i>+ (plus sign)</i> - New property</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p><i>- (minus sign)</i> - Removed property</p>
              </li>
            </ul></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><uicontrol>Name</uicontrol> - The property name.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><uicontrol>Current value</uicontrol> - The current value of the property.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><uicontrol>Base value</uicontrol> - The base (original) value of the property.</p>
        </li>
      </ul></p>
  </body>
</topic>